Package com.frdfsnlght.transporter.api

Interface Summary
Gate This interface specifies methods common to all gates managed by the Transporter plugin, whether local or remote.
LocalAreaGate Represents a local gate of the AREA type.
LocalBlockGate Represents a local gate of the BLOCK type.
LocalGate Represents a local gate on the local server.
LocalWorld Represents a world on the local server.
RealmPlayer This class represents a player record in the realm database.
RemoteAreaGate Represents an AREA gate on a remote server.
RemoteBlockGate Represents a BLOCK gate on a remote server.
RemoteGate Represents a gate on a remote server.
RemotePlayer Represents an online player on a remote server.
RemoteServer Represents a locally configured server that the plugin connects to.
RemoteWorld Represents a world on a remote server.
Reservation Represents a reservation to teleport an entity.
 

Class Summary
API This class provides the top level API for the Transporter plugin.
Callback<T> Represents a task to be executed after an asynchronous API call has completed.
RemoteLocation Represents a location in a remote world on a remote server.
 

Enum Summary
ExpandDirection Specifies directions a LocalAreaGate can be resized.
GateType Represents the type of gate.
SpawnDirection Specifies directions a LocalAreaGate will spawn and arriving player.
SpawnSearch Specifies directions a LocalAreaGate will search for a spawn location when a player arrives.
 

Exception Summary
GateException Represents an exception about a gate.
RemoteException Represents an exception about a remote API call.
ReservationException Represents an exception about a teleportation reservation.
TransporterException Base class for all Transporter exceptions.
